name: Donna Williamson
text: Papa Murphy's pizza is the best. I love this place. The employees are always so friendly.

name: Charles DeVore
text: Very courteous attendants. Pizza is very good. We will be back.

name: smilymommy carson
text:
Delicious and since we get to cook it ourselves it is hot every time.
Gluten free also.  Most of the workers were overly helpful and patient. Jason Lane is who speaks first to everyone and is always willing to help in any way. Kudos to you Mr. Lane.

name: Andy Theriot
text: Have purchased many pizzas from this location  but for some reason they really screwed up this time along with many times before.  Why do i go back.  Requested original crust but got diet crust, paid for an extra an ingredient but didn't get it.  Do the owners really care?  I don't think they do!

name: Brian Rodgers
text: So sad to hear that this location closed. This was a regular for our family.

name: JC Minton
text: Love their pizza! This location is always clean and the staff is friendly and helpful.

name: Darryl Peterson
text: I have always been pleased with the product and the service here.  I had a problem with a different Papa Murphy's location and they made it right.

name: Carmen h5 Guerra
text: Quick and easy meal for the kids and friendly staff.

name: Hazel Nichols
text: This place is always great and the ladies are always nice

name: Jody Hooven
text: Very friendly folks running this location and the pizza is really good.

name: Brendan Migliori
text: Hate the idea of paying $20 for crappy pizza that I have to bake.

name: Julia Kellogg
text: Yum! We won't ever get a pizza from anywhere else!  üçï
